    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>A Vine Strangler is a blighted plant creature that lurks beneath the ash and soil of the Ashen Woods. Its thorny tendrils erupt from the ground to constrict and drag prey underground. Patient and predatory, it waits motionless until warm-blooded creatures pass within reach.</p>",
      "director": "<p>The Vine Strangler starts hidden (Ambush feature). On its first turn, it erupts and uses Constrict with edge and +3 damage. On subsequent turns, it uses Drag Under to restrain grabbed targets, gaining cover while partially burrowed. If threatened, it can use Rootwalk to burrow away at speed 6 and reposition for another ambush. Target isolated PCs — especially casters at the edges of the group.</p>",
